title: Eurythmics - Live 1983 - 1989 TQMP
description:
Both Scottish, Annie Lennox and Dave Stuart are forming one of the most successful duos ever. Annie's distinctive voice and Dave's innovative production technics led to 75 millions records sold worldwide. They had a 10 years break in 90's, and they both had a successful solo career meanwhile, to reunite in 2001. During this break, in 1993 they released this album, a collection of their greatest hits performed live.

Enjoy!
